---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Create Your Free IncomeRecord.com Account"
  description="Create a free IncomeRecord.com account to save your stub history and employer profiles. Or use the free generator right now with no account required."
  canonical="https://incomerecord.com/signup"
>
  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <div class="max-w-md mx-auto mb-16">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Create Your Free IncomeRecord.com Account</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">Save your stub history and employer profiles.</p>

      <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm">
        <div class="mb-4 p-4 bg-yellow-50 border border-yellow-200 rounded-lg">
          <p class="text-yellow-800 text-sm"><strong>Coming Soon:</strong> Account creation launches with our Pro tier. The free pay stub generator at <a href="/" class="underline">incomerecord.com</a> is available right now with no account needed.</p>
        </div>

        <form class="space-y-4" action="#" method="POST">
          <div>
            <label for="name" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">Full name</label>
            <input
              type="text"
              id="name"
              name="name"
              autocomplete="name"
              placeholder="Jane Smith"
              class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-transparent"
            />
          </div>

          <div>
            <label for="email" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">Email address</label>
            <input
              type="email"
              id="email"
              name="email"
              autocomplete="email"
              placeholder="you@example.com"
              class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-transparent"
            />
          </div>

          <div>
            <label for="password" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">Password</label>
            <input
              type="password"
              id="password"
              name="password"
              autocomplete="new-password"
              placeholder="At least 8 characters"
              class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-transparent"
            />
          </div>

          <div>
            <label for="password_confirm" class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1">Confirm password</label>
            <input
              type="password"
              id="password_confirm"
              name="password_confirm"
              autocomplete="new-password"
              placeholder="Repeat your password"
              class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-transparent"
            />
          </div>

          <button
            type="submit"
            class="w-full bg-blue-600 text-white py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors"
          >
            Create Free Account
          </button>
        </form>

        <p class="text-center text-gray-600 mt-6 text-sm">
          Already have an account?
          <a href="/login" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700 font-medium">Log in</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <section class="border-t border-gray-200 pt-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Account vs. No Account: What's the Difference?</h2>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Without an Account (Available Now)</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-green-500 font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
              <span>Generate unlimited pay stubs instantly</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-green-500 font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
              <span>No watermarks on PDFs</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-green-500 font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
              <span>Download PDFs immediately</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-green-500 font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
              <span>No data stored anywhere — full privacy</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-green-500 font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
              <span>All 50 states, all pay frequencies</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-gray-300 font-bold mt-0.5">&#10007;</span>
              <span class="text-gray-500">No stub history — download when you generate</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-gray-300 font-bold mt-0.5">&#10007;</span>
              <span class="text-gray-500">No saved employer profiles</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">With a Free Account (Coming Soon)</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-green-500 font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
              <span>Everything without an account, plus:</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-green-500 font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
              <span>Access any stub you've ever generated</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-green-500 font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
              <span>Re-download stubs without regenerating</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-green-500 font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
              <span>Save one employer profile</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-green-500 font-bold mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
              <span>Basic dashboard with recent stubs</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <span class="text-yellow-600 font-bold mt-0.5">&#8594;</span>
              <span class="text-gray-600">Pro plan ($9/mo) adds unlimited saved employers, premium template, and more</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Who Creates Accounts?</h2>

      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">Most people who use IncomeRecord.com are generating documentation for a specific application — an apartment, a car loan, a mortgage. If that describes you, you probably don't need an account: generate the stub, download the PDF, use it in your application. Done.</p>

      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">Accounts make sense for people who generate pay stubs regularly:</p>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="p-5 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Regular Gig Workers</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">If you generate a monthly income statement for your records or to show consistent income to a housing authority or lender, an account means you don't retype employer information monthly.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-5 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Small Business Owners</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">If you pay yourself or a small number of employees and generate stubs each pay period, an account keeps your history organized and saves you from re-entering company information every time.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-5 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">People Who Lose Files</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">If you've ever needed a stub from two months ago and had to search through your downloads folder (or regenerate it from scratch), stub history solves that problem permanently.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-12 bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Just Need a Pay Stub Right Now?</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Skip the account — the free generator works immediately with no sign-up required.</p>
      <a href="/" class="inline-block bg-blue-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors">Generate a Pay Stub Free</a>
    </section>
  </main>
</Base>
